description:
CodePorting.Translator Cs2Cpp is a framework to automatically port code from C# to C++. The translated code can be compiled using Visual Studio, GCC or Clang and can run on Windows, Linux and MacOS.
	This package features an API used to emulate .Net calls from the translated code.
summary: The library to link against the code translated from C# to C++ CodePorting.Translator automated code translator
title: CodePorting.Translator Cs2Cpp Framework
